Variable.Name: CircIdx
Variable.Comment: Identification number of circuit (to set prevent List

Variable.Name: SuctP
Variable.Comment: Current suction pressure in Bars (relative value)

Variable.Name: DscgP
Variable.Comment: Current discharge pressure in Bars (relative value)

Variable.Name: DscgGasTemp
Variable.Comment: Current discharge temperature

Variable.Name: IsStep
Variable.Comment: TRUE: Step, FALSE: other compressor

Variable.Name: RfrgTyp
Variable.Comment: Gas type : see definition on T2P (FBD) help on line

Variable.Name: Zone
Variable.Comment: Envelop zone -> 0=Undefined, 1=Envelop zone, 2=EnvHiP_Ratio, 3=EnvHiDscgP, 4=EnvHiCurr, 5=EnvHiSuctP, 6=EnvLowP_Ratio, 7=EnvLowDP, 8=EnvLowDscgP, 9=EnvLowSuctP

Variable.Name: EnvP_X
Variable.Comment: Vertex points of envelop (X values) in degrees C

Variable.Name: EnvP_Y
Variable.Comment: Vertex points of envelop (Y values) in tenth of degrees C

Variable.Name: CfgEnv
Variable.Comment: Segment data of envelope working zones in degrees C

Variable.Name: Cfg_CompStep
Variable.Comment: Data of step configurations

Variable.Name: HeatMode
Variable.Comment: Working mode: 0=chiller; 1= HP - used for selection of standard slope of movement

Variable.Name: InPwr
Variable.Comment: Input request

Variable.Name: GotoPwrSetP
Variable.Comment: Set output power value equal to power input value

Variable.Name: CompPh
Variable.Comment: Compressor phase : 0=OFF; 1= StartUp; 2=StarUp incr.;3=Increase; 4=StandBy; 5=Decrease;6=unused;7=ShutOffdecr.; 8=ShutOff

Variable.Name: DecelDist
Variable.Comment: Distance from envelope limit border in which starts deceleration of power increasing

Variable.Name: MinPwrCorr
Variable.Comment: minimum value of output when correcting to meet envelope conditions

Variable.Name: UpDeltaMaxPwr
Variable.Comment: Maximum request variation percentage per second up

Variable.Name: DwnDeltaMaxPwr
Variable.Comment: Maximum request variation per second down

Variable.Name: HiTemp_PwrStepDwn
Variable.Comment: Power step down in case in case of HT

Variable.Name: HiTemp_ActionWait
Variable.Comment: conteggio ritardo in atto inibisce nuova azione per ridurre HT

Variable.Name: DscgGasActZone
Variable.Comment: Distance from discharge gas HT limit in which starts deceleration of power increasing

Variable.Name: PreventT
Variable.Comment: Time duration of prevent action (reduction /increasing of step power) - def. 120s

Variable.Name: TransdStart
Variable.Comment: Initial condition that inhibites correction of zone 9 (for HP starting -up )

Variable.Name: PreventInfoIn
Variable.Comment: Prevent list to Rot_Dev

Variable.Name: CompReq
Variable.Comment: Compressor On status

Variable.Name: OutPwr
Variable.Comment: Output request - considering slide movements (simulated)

Variable.Name: MOPThrshFastChg
Variable.Comment: Current Value of MOP to EVD - Value in degrees C

Variable.Name: RunPrevent
Variable.Comment: Prevent action in execution for power reduction or increasing

Variable.Name: PreventInfo
Variable.Comment: Prevent list to Rot_Dev

Variable.Name: EvapTemp
Variable.Comment: Current suction saturated temperature C

Variable.Name: CondTemp
Variable.Comment: Current discharge saturated temperature C

Variable.Name: DeltaP
Variable.Comment: Current value of delta pressure [Bars]

Variable.Name: DeltaMinP
Variable.Comment: Minumum difference between discharge pressure and suction pressure [Bars]

Variable.Name: RatioP
Variable.Comment: current value of pressure ratio

Variable.Name: Distance
Variable.Comment: the value of the distance used for the request calculation

Variable.Name: EnvDirectDistance
Variable.Comment: Distance long interpolation line and movement direction to P1 in degrees C

Variable.Name: EnvOppositeDistance
Variable.Comment: Distance long interpolation line and opposite direction to P2 in degrees C

Variable.Name: ZoneDscgTemp
Variable.Comment: Discharge gas HT control 0=Unchecked; 1=OK; 2 = Action zone (pwr controlled); 3=HT condition (power limited); 4= Max temp (alarm)

Variable.Name: ZoneMaxCap
Variable.Comment: envelope zone with limited max capacity - due to critical lubricating pressure

Variable.Name: HiTempActionDone
Variable.Comment: Eseguita riduzione del 10% sulla potenza

Variable.Name: EvapRegTempSetP
Variable.Comment: Current value of Evaporating temp. limit (Fan regul. in Pdc) - Value in degrees C

Variable.Name: CondRegTempSetP
Variable.Comment: Current value of Condensing temp. limit (Fan regul. in chiller) - Value in degrees C

Variable.Name: DscgHiTempThrsh
Variable.Comment: Discharge gas HT limit over which power is reduced (5K below alarm limit)

Variable.Name: EnvEvapMaxTemp
Variable.Comment: Suction saturated temp high limit - Value C

Variable.Name: EnvEvapMinTemp
Variable.Comment: Suction saturated temp low limit - Value C

Variable.Name: EnvCondMaxTemp
Variable.Comment: Discharge saturated temp high limit - Value C

Variable.Name: EnvCondMinTemp
Variable.Comment: Discharge saturated temp low limit - Value C

Variable.Name: Ka
Variable.Comment: Interpolation line, explicit form coefficient (trend from last 5 recorded temperature points)

Variable.Name: Kb
Variable.Comment: Interpolation line, explicit form coefficient (trend from last 5 recorded temperature points)

Variable.Name: Kc
Variable.Comment: Interpolation line, explicit form coefficient (trend from last 5 recorded temperature points)

Variable.Name: Km
Variable.Comment: Interpolation line, implicit form (slope coefficent)

Variable.Name: Kq
Variable.Comment: Interpolation line, implicit form (slope coefficent)

Variable.Name: StartPhase
Variable.Comment: Starting condition that overcomes power control

Variable.Name: EnvMaxCap
Variable.Comment: min value of condensing setPoint for fan speed control when in max cap zone

Variable.Name: SumX
Variable.Comment: the sum of all the sampled x values

Variable.Name: SumY
Variable.Comment: the sum of all the sampled y values

Variable.Name: SumSquareX
Variable.Comment: the sum of all the sampled x^2 values

Variable.Name: SumXY
Variable.Comment: Sum (Xi*Yi)

Variable.Comment: Zone out of envelope - segment of high current -> Zone=4
